Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机翼开始轰鸣的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太平无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天因为工作，我会晚些回来\N祝你考试顺利——妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该是“今天”，应该是“今天也”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池袋…池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在那儿的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在发什么呆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，怎么原来是你啊朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说“怎么原来是你”太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的跟班呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人在盯着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇？是狗仔队吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很受欢迎啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我感觉良好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！讨厌！要迟到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，快点吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君，快点！快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点！啊，鸟饲！等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最坏的情形是他们可能有过接触了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上发布紧急搜索令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一道防线好像已经被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳和氧气反应生成二氧化碳\N能赶得上吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个碳原子和氧气化合成两个一氧化碳\N“会不会迟到”这种事想了也没有用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经这个时候了，你就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“临阵磨枪，不快也光”吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用功是给别人看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你就会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实连神名君也会有努力的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习画画的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来指望朝比奈这样的普通人能够\N理解这种事情是不可能的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩子，别和绫人捣乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，男人总是互相护短
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，实验中心方面会派其他人去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按这个指示执行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要调动军事直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，守！守！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈！朝比奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名…君…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟饲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟饲？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照看好守！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就去找人来帮忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到人我就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君！神名君！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？！一个人都没有？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的平民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真碍事,闪开！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍一下！你也是个男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，就这么点伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我根本找不到人去帮助他们！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rah——-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！你！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在那里太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲香…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙汁可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算缓过劲来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战争吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，很意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会在这里遇到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为神名君这么突然地出现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，无论如何，还算不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人总比一个人强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在那个地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，难道你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在出去还很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Dolem
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.07,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dolem：MU的人型兵器，又被称为D-1
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必为他担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉…大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉，我真是个笨蛋，竟然会问你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在消灭敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说那是防卫军的秘密武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，这里的确很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们动用了“那个”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为首都防卫的核心的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bingo！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样妥当吗？动用Allegretto？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:08.28,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Allegretto：音乐名词，指“小块板”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它那方面不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有olin它无法觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.58,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}olin：那瓦克神话名词，这里指RahXephon的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使觉醒了，也无法歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现olin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是神名 绫人君吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是政府派来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有更多的时间解释
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能跟我们走一趟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要给我个解释…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太顽固了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见啰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以算是正义的使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，我救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少该说声“谢谢”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在危险之中救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“为什么他们的血是蓝色的？”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你跟我来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色血的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对年长的女性没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让女性蒙羞可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什公正义的使者！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了，行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，绫人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在发车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意正在关闭的车门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
