Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对会保护美屿你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
