Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的Dolem！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rah——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快觉醒吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rah…
